# UI Guidelines

## Design System

Material UI.

---

## Navigation

Top AppBar.

Menu items:

- Search
- Settings

---

## Search Page Layout

Container

Search Form

Results List

---

## Settings Page Layout

Container

Header

Add Website Button

Website List

---

## Loading States

Use:

- CircularProgress

---

## Empty States

Use:

Typography

Examples:

"No news found"

"No websites configured"

---

## Dialogs

Use MUI Dialog.

Required:

- Add Website Dialog
- Edit Website Dialog
- Delete Confirmation Dialog

---

## Notifications

Use MUI Snackbar.

Display all success and error messages.

---

## Accessibility

All interactive controls must have labels.

Keyboard navigation supported.

Dialogs must trap focus.